title: Grateful Dead Live at Providence Civic Center on 1980-09-04
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Peggy-O, Cassidy, Dire Wolf, Minglewood Blues, Althea, Looks Like Rain, Far From Me, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Ramble On Rose, Supplication-> Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Good Lovin', E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: Underestimated Prophet The most underrated show I have ever been too.
